    <p>
        Features on the website:
    <ul>
        <li>Five stocks on the watchlist by default. </li>
        <li>Data loads once for first time visitor. The watchlist, price info together with a timestamp are
            stored in localstorage</li>
        <li>Return user (same day) will get watchlist, price info and data from localstorage.</li>
        <li>Regardless of user status, the day will reload each day on the first visit.</li>
        <li>User can amend the watchlist (add or delete), the localstorge is updated to reflect the changes.</li>
        <li>User can delete stock by selecting the symbol first.</li>
        <li>Watch list symbols are unique.</li>
        <li>Green and Red color reflect the positive and negative % change in price.</li>
        <li>Select a stock, the news will be related to the company/symbol.</li>
        <li>Without stock selection, there are random financial news.</li>
        <li>A compound interest calculator, it assumes the monthly contribution is made at the end of each month.</li>
    </ul>
